  "texts": [
    "This shows that SSEHCET helps to improve the security of healthcare data transmission and storage.",
    "Ease of learning/usability evaluation of SSEHCETThe questionnaire used in the case study involved four questions related to the ease of learning and usability evaluation of SSEHCET.",
    "The weighted average of all four questions was above 3.5, which shows that the proposed model can be learned easily after a few hours of training.",
    "The results shown in Fig. 11 highlight the positive elements of the ease of learning connected with SSEHCET.",
    "This evaluation was conducted using a well-designed questionnaire consisting of four relevant items."
  ]
}